text: Vineet is an Indian name. It may refer to: *Vineet Alurkar, Indian musician *Vineet M. Arora, American medical researcher *Vineet Jain, Managing director and Director of Bennett, Coleman & Co. Ltd. *Vineet Jain (cricketer), Indian cricketer *Vineet Kothari, Indian judge *Vineet Kumar, Indian actor ==References== Category:Indian masculine given names
title: Vineet
